properties.Description:
The D&B PAYDEX Score provides instant overview of how a firm pays its bills as reported to D&B.  This helps you determine how quickly they're likely to pay you. The PAYDEX is a 1-100 dollar weighted numerical score of payment performance, calculated using up to 875 payment experiences from trade references reported to D&B.

D&B PAYDEX Score Key Use this Key to help you determine the meaning of the Score.
